          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>End the Partisan IRS Culture Act or the EPIC Act</strong></p> <p>This bill excludes employees of the Internal Revenue Service from provisions of federal personnel law allowing federal employees to organize, bargain collectively, and participate in labor organizations. </p>]]></text>
